<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 12:21:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国参议院委员会审议针对中国华大基因、药明康德的法案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-senate-committee-takes-up-bill-targeting-chinas-bgi-wuxi-apptec-2024-03-06/</link><description>美国参议院一项以国家安全为由限制与中国华大基因、药明康德和其他生物科技公司开展业务的法案将于周三在国会面临首次重大考验。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 11:07:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-senate-committee-takes-up-bill-targeting-chinas-bgi-wuxi-apptec-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鲍威尔在大盘分散后开盘</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-06/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 11:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国抱怨荷兰有关台湾的新闻报道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-complains-about-dutch-news-report-taiwan-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国周三对荷兰公共广播公司 NOS 对台湾的一则新闻报道表示不满，这表明北京对台湾的立场变得更强硬。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 10:41:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-complains-about-dutch-news-report-taiwan-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>京东季度收入超出预期，大幅折扣提振需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-e-commerce-firm-jdcom-beats-fourth-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-03-06/</link><description>京东(JD.com)，周三在美国盘前交易中股价上涨12%，此前这家中国在线零售商公布的第四季度营收高于预期，并宣布将扩大股票回购计划的规模。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 10:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-e-commerce-firm-jdcom-beats-fourth-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>西门子高管表示，随着经济繁荣，西门子对印度寄予厚望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/siemens-has-high-hopes-india-economy-booms-executive-says-2024-03-06/</link><description>西门子董事会成员马蒂亚斯·雷贝利乌斯(Matthias Rebellius)表示，西门子对其在印度的前景“非常乐观”，因为该国经济蓬勃发展，并提供了摆脱中国业务多元化的机会。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 09:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/siemens-has-high-hopes-india-economy-booms-executive-says-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，摩根士丹利因市场暴跌而削减了9%的中国基金部门员工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/morgan-stanley-cuts-9-china-fund-unit-staff-amid-market-rout-sources-say-2024-03-06/</link><description>两位直接了解情况的人士表示，摩根士丹利已解雇其在中国的资产管理业务部门约 9% 的员工，因为中国不断上涨的股市削弱了其 3.8 万亿美元基金部门的前景。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 08:03:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/morgan-stanley-cuts-9-china-fund-unit-staff-amid-market-rout-sources-say-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>国家规划师称中国2024年5%的增长目标可实现</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-step-up-economic-policy-adjustments-2024-state-planner-says-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国国家规划负责人周三表示，中国政府今年5%的经济增长目标是可以实现的，许多分析人士认为这个目标雄心勃勃，他预计世界第二大经济体第一季度将有良好表现。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 08:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-step-up-economic-policy-adjustments-2024-state-planner-says-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾总统表示，南海碰撞不是援引与美国防务条约的理由</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-china-sea-collision-not-reason-invoke-defence-treaty-with-us-says-2024-03-06/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周三表示，最近菲律宾和中国船只在南海发生的相撞事件不是启动与美国签署共同防御条约的时机或理由。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 07:26:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-china-sea-collision-not-reason-invoke-defence-treaty-with-us-says-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>东盟和澳大利亚呼吁停止在南海破坏稳定的行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asean-australia-call-an-end-destabilising-actions-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</link><description>周三，澳大利亚和东盟在为期三天的峰会结束时发表联合声明，称所有国家都应避免在南海采取危及争议地区和平、安全与稳定的单方面行动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:39:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asean-australia-call-an-end-destabilising-actions-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>总统称斯里兰卡承诺在2027年至2042年期间偿还债务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sri-lanka-committed-repaying-debt-within-2027-2042-schedule-president-says-2024-03-06/</link><description>斯里兰卡总统拉尼尔·维克勒马辛哈周三表示，斯里兰卡致力于在2027年至2042年的时间表内偿还债务，并补充说，成功的债务重组谈判将使年度外债支付额降至GDP的4%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:26:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sri-lanka-committed-repaying-debt-within-2027-2042-schedule-president-says-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国能否同时保持增长和“转型”经济？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/can-china-maintain-growth-transform-its-economy-same-time-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国总理李强的国家愿景存在一个内在的矛盾：他“转变”经济模式的目标可能与保持增长率稳定在5%左右不相容。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:14:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/can-china-maintain-growth-transform-its-economy-same-time-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>对西方白酒制造商来说，挑战中国国酒是一项艰巨的任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/challenging-chinas-national-drink-is-tall-order-western-liquor-makers-2024-03-06/</link><description>寻求利用中国年轻饮酒者对威士忌和干邑白兰地日益增长的需求的全球饮料巨头在与中国主导白酒生产商的竞争中面临着挑战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:11:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/challenging-chinas-national-drink-is-tall-order-western-liquor-makers-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾指责中国在南海“挑起事端”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-deliberately-stirring-up-trouble-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</link><description>菲律宾高级安全官员周三表示，本周与北京在南海发生的戏剧性对峙是菲律宾迄今为止最严重的事件，并誓言在维护菲律宾主权方面不会退缩。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 05:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-deliberately-stirring-up-trouble-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>由于工厂陷入困境，中国一月至二月出口可能放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-jan-feb-factories-struggle-2024-03-06/</link><description>路透周三的一项调查显示，中国一月至二月的出口增长可能放缓，这表明制造商仍在为海外买家而苦苦挣扎，并需要国内进一步的政策支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 05:36:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-likely-slowed-jan-feb-factories-struggle-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚对南海破坏稳定的行为表示担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-concerned-about-destabilising-behaviour-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</link><description>周三，中国和菲律宾船只在争议海域发生冲突的第二天，澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞表示，澳大利亚非常关注南海的不安全和破坏稳定的行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 05:29:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-concerned-about-destabilising-behaviour-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>